
---

# .gitignore

Para SDL3 + CMake + VSCode:

```gitignore
# Build folders
build/
build-web/
bin/
out/

# CMake
CMakeCache.txt
CMakeLists.txt.DotSettings.user
CMakeFiles/
cmake_install.cmake
compile_commands.json
Makefile

# Ninja
.ninja_deps
.ninja_log

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.sln
*.vcxproj
*.vcxproj.user

# VSCode
.vscode/

# CLion
.idea/

# Executables
*.exe
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib

# Debug
*.pdb

# Logs
*.log

# Emscripten
*.wasm
*.data
*.js
*.html

# Temporary
*.tmp
*.cache

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
